I have had the fortune of working within the Audio Video industry for nearly a decade, the majority of which has been with Best Buy. I started my career with Best Buy in 2003 at the Sugar Land location as a part time associate in Home Theater.  As my passion for higher end audio/video grew, I rose in the ranks from my part time role to one of the elite Magnolia Professionals in 2007. I was given the opportunity to work closely with our home entertainment advisors to build custom experiences for my clients, which furthered my interest in higher end solutions.  Getting the best quality from a professional is important to me, which is why I strive to give nothing short of the best experience for all of my clients based on their needs.  Working in the Magnolia Design Center located in the heart of the Austin area has allowed me to further focus on client experience, just as Magnolia has for the past half century. It is with this shared vision of 100% satisfaction that I look forward to many more years within this field that I am so passionate about.
